com.freshbourne.multimap.btree
Class BTree<K,V>

java.lang.Object
  com.freshbourne.multimap.btree.BTree<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K -
V -
All Implemented Interfaces:
ComplexPage, MustInitializeOrLoad, MultiMap<K,V>
public class BTree<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiMap<K,V>, ComplexPage

An implementation of a Map that can hold more that one value for each key. This class does all the rotating and balancing of the BTree so that Leafs and InnerNodes are not polluted by having to create new nodes. This is done exclusively in this class.
